cz.cuni.mff.kocur.base

Class GraphicResources

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.cuni.mff.kocur.base.GraphicResources

  • public class GraphicResources
extends java.lang.Object
    This class will contain all the graphic resources like images, icons etc. I might need. This is helpful because I don't need to load them each time I want to use them and I might share them (e. g. icons for buttons). I am not loading everything - I am using hash maps to load icons only at the time they are used.
    Author:
    kocur
